      <title>협업을 위한 더러운 코드</title>
      <link>https://blog.blu3fishez.org/posts/2024/2024-12-21-%ED%98%91%EC%97%85%EC%9D%84-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%9C-%EB%8D%94%EB%9F%AC%EC%9A%B4-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C/</link>
